            </div>
            <div class="pt-3 px-5 ml-5">
                <p class="text-white small my-0"><i class="fas fa-address-book text-danger"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;投前管理决策</p>
                <p class="text-white small my-0"><i class="fas fa-address-book text-danger"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;投后投模管理</p>
                <p class="text-white small my-0"><i class="fas fa-address-book text-danger"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;全面预算管理</p>
                <p class="text-white small my-0"><i class="fas fa-address-book text-danger"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;B&nbsp;&nbsp;I&nbsp;&nbsp;决策分析</p>
                <p class="text-white small my-0"><i class="fas fa-address-book text-danger"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;财报税务分析</p>
            </div>
            <div class="m-5">
                <p class="text-white small">
                    <span>更多帮助信息 请登录官网查询 <a href="http://www.kuanfang.cn/" title="官网网址" target="_blank">WWW.KUANFANG.CN</a></span>
